{"tid":619292,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)凶兆 閃靈 鬼玩人2013","createTime":"2018-04-06T13:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T18:12:36.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"077f06132f9062268c9ebaea55e6e5ec62d8255a","tid":619292,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:32:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=UbW2vO8m7x9JLRryiFjPLtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=acacac48\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=UbW2vO8m7x9JLRryiFjPLtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=3a93e1d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.screengeek.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/sinister-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.screengeek.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2Fsinister-3.jpg&h=e00994c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9aeb650920151ec393d99154e70abdda_hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic1.zhimg.com%2F50%2Fv2-9aeb650920151ec393d99154e70abdda_hd.jpg&h=983979b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9d/EvilDead2013Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9d%2FEvilDead2013Poster.jpg&h=cb04f6fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1. 過氣的暢銷犯罪作家艾利森專門撰寫一些真實的犯罪事件，為了要獲得靈感，再寫一部暢銷書改善家境，瞞著全家人搬到一間兇宅裡去，要寫一件全家人被吊死，而小女兒失蹤的滅門事件...<br />\n<br />\n2.傑克&middot;托倫斯(Jack Torrance)是一名作家，為了擺脫工作上的失意，接受了一份在冬天維護科羅拉多州一家奢華的山間飯店的工作。他年幼的兒子擁有通靈能力，能夠看到過去和未來的東西，如棲息在飯店的鬼魂。到飯店安頓好後不久，這家人就被暴風雪困住了，傑克逐漸受到一個超自然的存在的影響；他陷入瘋狂並企圖謀殺他的妻子和兒子<br />\n<br />\n3.有毒癮問題的米亞與哥哥及親友們一塊到郊區小木屋度假，而他們意外在屋內的地窖中發現了一本名為「死亡之書」的神祕書籍！不料，卻喚醒了附近樹林的妖魔鬼怪，這群人慘遭惡魔附身展開血腥大屠殺，最後倖存的一人，能否順利逃出且活著離開？<br />\n<br />\n9 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=UbW2vO8m7x9JLRryiFjPLtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=497de144\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=UbW2vO8m7x9JLRryiFjPLtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=ff449bf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28268b901b44e5c9503fdfe681bd68351768372","tid":619292,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97824814d99cbef0689ec3273fcff99d80f19af3","tid":619292,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fbb6e04907122d17908d5853ee6c3100a413f6c","tid":619292,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":